UEFA Europa League Highlights 2016-04-14 ITV HDTV 1080p 2ch x265 [S-Less]

Action from the quarter-final second-leg ties, featuring Liverpool v Borussia Dortmund at Anfield, Sevilla v Athletic Bilbao at the Estadio Ramon Sanchez Pizjuan, Shakhtar Donetsk v SC Braga at the Arena Lviv and Sparta Prague v Villarreal at the Stadion Letna. Presented by Mark Pougatch, with analysis from Glenn Hoddle.
